<p><a name="Further_reading" id="Further_reading"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Codex&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/David_Diringer" title="David Diringer">David Diringer</a>, <i>The Book Before Printing: Ancient, Medieval and Oriental</i>, Courier Dover Publications, New York 1982, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0486242439" class="internal">ISBN 0486242439</a></li>
<li>C. H. Roberts – T. C. Skeat, <i>The Birth of the Codex</i>, Oxford University Press, New York – Cambridge 1983.</li>
<li>L. W. Hurtado, <i>The Earliest Christian Artifacts: Manuscripts and Christian Origins</i>, Cambridge 2006.</li>
</ul>
